BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:QCYk8EufG66SXyONhd-B5
SUMMARY:Women's Day Out: Shop\, Sip & Self-Care
DTSTAMP:20260314T071049Z
DTSTART:20260314T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day of pampering\, wellness\, fitness and shoppin
	g as we celebrate the importance of self-care!\n\n✨ Women’s Day Out: Sip\,
	 Shop & Self-Care ✨\n\nJoin us on Saturday\, March 14 at The Winemakers Re
	serve in Woodinville for a day designed to refresh your mind\, body\, and 
	soul!\n\n  \n\n💆‍♀️ Pamper yourself with spa \\+ wellness services\n\n🧠 Disco
	ver resources to support your mental & physical health\n\n🛍️ Shop unique fi
	nds from local businesses\n\n🎁 Enter exciting giveaways & door prizes\n\n🎉
	 Enjoy fun surprises throughout the day\n\n🧁 Indulge in delicious sweet tr
	eats\n\n🎶 Relax or groove to live music\n\n  \n\n…and we are bringing back
	 fitness & wellness classes for our VIP ticket holders!\n\nCome solo\, wit
	h your girlfriends\, spouse\, or a loved one—you’ll leave feeling refreshe
	d and inspired!\n\n  \n\nWhile this event is designed with women in mind\,
	 all are welcome to join the celebration.\n\n  \n\nBOGO Tickets available 
	through January 20th!\n\nRegular Admission: $13.80\n\nVIP Admission: $49.6
	4\n\nVIPs will receive a complimentary glass of wine\, access to four clas
	ses\, and a swag bag valued at $200\\+.\n\nInterested in being a vendor? W
	e’d love to hear from women-focused businesses like you! Apply at https://
	docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdh9BT04UZ0j3RnIfOmOou\\_pR6vS3knbxFfPp4m
	J2ZTZ6oJfw/viewform?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwN
	TU4AAGnpyixJNHPOOzJHYreNrcM7WCCFclxIWxTeIYeuu8ClTmuhBD7Ft4QlzU3brg\\_aem\\
	_0jikthn12Lbt8b8XyhFyEQ\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/w
	omen-s-day-out-shop-sip-self-care/18291080/2026-03-14T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday 
	- Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/women-s-day-out-shop-sip-
	self-care/18291080/2026-03-14T00
LOCATION:The Winemakers Reserve\, 15902 Woodinville-Redmond Rd NE\, Suite D
	\, Woodinville\, WA
